<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Top-level tour -- Japan's Prime Minister Noboru Takeshita waves goodby 
after a 30-minute visit to residents of the Japanese Retirement Home in Boyle 
Heights on Sunday. ROBERT DURELL / Los Angeles Times 
